301
00:37:58,343 --> 00:38:00,073
But there wasn't
any other path

302
00:38:01,012 --> 00:38:03,122
Come back, Mei

303
00:38:04,182 --> 00:38:05,912
Mei, back

304
00:38:18,730 --> 00:38:21,770
But it's true Totoro was here

305
00:38:22,934 --> 00:38:24,454
I'm not lying

306
00:38:33,545 --> 00:38:34,945
1 know, Mei

307
00:38:35,280 --> 00:38:36,650
I didnt lie

308
00:38:38,583 --> 00:38:42,093
Neither of us think
you're lying

309
00:38:42,720 --> 00:38:45,680
You probably met
the king of this forest

310
00:38:46,224 --> 00:38:48,064
You were very lucky

311
00:38:49,027 --> 00:38:51,427
He doesnt come out very often

312
00:38:53,331 --> 00:38:55,521
We should go to the shrine
to pay our respects

313
00:38:55,967 --> 00:38:56,577
Pay our respects?

314
00:38:56,801 --> 00:38:58,171
To this forest

315
00:39:16,521 --> 00:39:17,831
Mei, you're getting heavy

316
00:39:18,156 --> 00:39:19,826
Daddy, look
That camphor tree

317
00:39:21,025 --> 00:39:22,315
What a big tree

318
00:39:30,635 --> 00:39:31,685
It's here

319
00:39:32,770 --> 00:39:34,060
Is that the tree?

320
00:39:34,873 --> 00:39:36,773
Dad, hurry up

321
00:39:48,253 --> 00:39:49,803
The hole has gone

322
00:39:50,154 --> 00:39:51,354
Are you sure it was here?

323
00:39:53,258 --> 00:39:54,928
The hole disappeared

324
00:39:56,160 --> 00:39:57,620
! told you he doesnt
come fo see us often

325
00:39:57,962 --> 00:39:59,012
But, will he come again?

326
00:39:59,297 --> 00:40:00,907
1 want to meet him, too

327
00:40:01,266 --> 00:40:03,846
If you're lucky, sure

328
00:40:05,536 --> 00:40:07,086
What a beautiful tree

329
00:40:08,873 --> 00:40:12,473
This tree must have stood
here for years and years

330
00:40:14,579 --> 00:40:17,739
Trees and people
used to be good friends

331
00:40:19,651 --> 00:40:23,341
! saw that tree and
decided to buy the house

332
00:40:23,988 --> 00:40:26,238
Hope Mom likes it too

333
00:40:26,691 --> 00:40:28,151
Okay, let's pay our respects

334
00:40:28,493 --> 00:40:29,663
then get home for lunch

335
00:40:29,961 --> 00:40:30,691
Oh yeah

336
00:40:30,929 --> 00:40:32,359
! promised
to go see Michiko

337
00:40:32,697 --> 00:40:34,067
! want to go, too

338
00:40:34,399 --> 00:40:35,709
Attention

339
00:40:36,034 --> 00:40:39,984
Thank you for
looking after Mei

340
00:40:40,672 --> 00:40:42,402
Thank you very much

341
00:40:43,641 --> 00:40:44,951
Last one home's
a rotten egg

342
00:40:45,276 --> 00:40:46,705
That's not fair, Dad

343
00:40:47,645 --> 00:40:48,634
Wait

344
00:40:50,815 --> 00:40:51,985
Hurry up

345
00:40:52,684 --> 00:40:54,294
Wait for me

346
00:40:57,055 --> 00:40:57,694
Dear Mother

347
00:40:57,922 --> 00:40:59,882
Something amazing
happened today

348
00:41:00,291 --> 00:41:02,921
Mei met a giant Totoro

349
00:41:08,766 --> 00:41:12,306
And I'm hoping to see
him myself soon, too

350
00:41:43,134 --> 00:41:45,854
Kanta, hurry up
You'll be late

351
00:41:46,371 --> 00:41:47,271
Coming

352
00:42:29,947 --> 00:42:30,847
Mei?

353
00:42:31,749 --> 00:42:32,618
Excuse me

354
00:42:32,884 --> 00:42:34,054
Yes, Satsuki?

355
00:42:34,986 --> 00:42:36,536
It's my sister

356
00:42:43,928 --> 00:42:45,538
What happened, Nanny?

357
00:42:45,897 --> 00:42:47,096
I'm sorry

358
00:42:47,398 --> 00:42:50,298
She insisted that
she be with you

359
00:42:50,835 --> 00:42:54,705
It's Dad's day
at the university

360
00:42:55,373 --> 00:42:58,213
You promised to be
a good girl at Nanny's

361
00:43:01,345 --> 00:43:03,185
! still have two more classes

362
00:43:03,581 --> 00:43:05,571
and Nanny'’s too busy for this

363
00:43:05,983 --> 00:43:09,733
