I'll go talk to my teacher

365
00:43:26,604 --> 00:43:30,614
Since Satsuki's mother
is in the hospital

366
00:43:31,309 --> 00:43:33,269
! want you alf
to be nice to her

367
00:43:33,678 --> 00:43:34,877
Yes

368
00:43:40,918 --> 00:43:42,228
What's that?

369
00:43:42,553 --> 00:43:43,633
It's Totoro

370
00:43:45,623 --> 00:43:47,143
Mei, you should keep quiet

371
00:43:47,492 --> 00:43:48,342
Okay

372
00:43:58,936 --> 00:44:00,636
Bye bye, Mei

373
