374
00:44:04,041 --> 00:44:05,301
We'll let teacher know

375
00:44:05,610 --> 00:44:07,360
See you

376
00:44:08,813 --> 00:44:10,273
Hurry up, it's going to rain

377
00:44:10,615 --> 00:44:11,544
Okay

378
00:44:19,924 --> 00:44:20,824
Here it comes

379
00:44:33,237 --> 00:44:33,877
Here

380
00:44:38,042 --> 00:44:40,122
! won't cry. Aren't l good?

381
00:44:43,080 --> 00:44:44,950
It's getting worse

382
00:44:47,752 --> 00:44:48,602
Dear Guardian Spirit

383
00:44:48,853 --> 00:44:50,693
let us stay
until the rain stops

384
00:45:34,799 --> 00:45:35,819
But...

385
00:45:56,420 --> 00:45:57,970
That was lucky

386
00:45:59,557 --> 00:46:01,287
It's got holes in it

387
00:46:13,471 --> 00:46:15,461
Daddy forgot his umbrella

388
00:46:15,873 --> 00:46:17,183
I'm going, too

389
00:46:20,911 --> 00:46:22,521
! said I forgot it

390
00:46:22,880 --> 00:46:26,130
