umbrella on a rainy day?

391
00:46:26,717 --> 00:46:28,057
Ouch

392
00:46:28,386 --> 00:46:30,286
You broke it playing, I bet

393
00:46:30,688 --> 00:46:31,648
1 did not

394
00:46:45,136 --> 00:46:46,396
Excuse me

395
00:46:49,073 --> 00:46:50,883
Hello, Satsuki, Mei

396
00:46:51,275 --> 00:46:52,445
Grandma

397
00:46:54,145 --> 00:46:55,455
I'm sorry about Mei today

398
00:46:55,780 --> 00:46:57,650
Not at all
Sorry we couldn't do more

399
00:46:58,049 --> 00:47:00,799
Kanta lent us this umbrella

400
00:47:02,019 --> 00:47:03,249
He did?

401
00:47:03,554 --> 00:47:05,014
A broken old thing like that

402
00:47:05,356 --> 00:47:07,346
Mei was with me, so I was glad

403
00:47:07,758 --> 00:47:09,567
But I'm so sorry
that Kanta got wet

404
00:47:09,960 --> 00:47:11,300
Thank you very much

405
00:47:11,629 --> 00:47:12,449
Not at all

406
00:47:12,697 --> 00:47:16,267
It probably
cleaned him up a little

407
00:47:16,901 --> 00:47:18,131
Are you off to
meet your father?

408
00:47:18,436 --> 00:47:20,626
Yes
What good girls you are

409
00:47:21,072 --> 00:47:22,332
Bye bye, Mei

410
00:47:22,640 --> 00:47:23,720
Bye bye

411
00:47:34,185 --> 00:47:35,645
Who was that?

412
00:47:35,986 --> 00:47:37,006
I don't know

413
00:47:41,826 --> 00:47:42,876
Just in time

414
00:47:56,440 --> 00:47:57,520
Getting on?

415
00:47:59,143 --> 00:48:00,543
All right, drive on

416
00:48:09,253 --> 00:48:11,063
Daddy wasnt on it

417
00:48:11,455 --> 00:48:13,185
He'll be on the next one

418
00:48:13,557 --> 00:48:15,136
Why don't you wait at Nanny's?

419
00:48:51,762 --> 00:48:52,962
Are you okay?

420
00:49:24,929 --> 00:49:27,389
Mei, sleepy?

421
00:49:28,833 --> 00:49:32,023
I told you
Wanna go to Nanny's?

422
00:49:34,905 --> 00:49:35,725
It won't be much longer

423
00:49:35,973 --> 00:49:36,993
Hang in there

424
00:49:43,180 --> 00:49:44,930
It's late

425
00:49:53,290 --> 00:49:54,220
Come on

426
00:51:18,142 --> 00:51:19,042
Are you Totoro?

427
00:51:29,820 --> 00:51:30,690
Wait a minute

428
00:51:36,694 --> 00:51:37,714
You can use this

429
00:51:39,263 --> 00:51:41,403
Take it, Mei's slipping off

430
00:51:47,938 --> 00:51:49,308
Hold it like this

431
00:53:06,483 --> 00:53:07,503
Here's the bus

432
00:54:15,252 --> 00:54:18,152
