433
00:54:31,969 --> 00:54:33,309
I'm sorry

434
00:54:33,637 --> 00:54:34,927
All right, drive on

435
00:54:35,506 --> 00:54:36,796
The train was late

436
00:54:37,107 --> 00:54:38,567
and I missed the bus

437
00:54:39,309 --> 00:54:40,679
Were you worried?

438
00:54:41,445 --> 00:54:43,465
We met him, Dad
He was here

439
00:54:43,881 --> 00:54:45,661
And the cat bus

440
00:54:46,049 --> 00:54:47,129
What?

441
00:54:47,417 --> 00:54:48,817
It was huge

442
00:54:49,153 --> 00:54:50,792
With big eyes like these

443
00:54:51,155 --> 00:54:52,525
We met him

444
00:54:54,057 --> 00:54:58,067
We met Totoro

445
00:54:58,762 --> 00:55:00,222
How wonderful

446
00:55:11,975 --> 00:55:13,025
Come on, Daddy

447
00:55:21,351 --> 00:55:22,111
Dear Mother

448
00:55:22,352 --> 00:55:24,721
I cant tell you
how excited I was today

449
00:55:25,189 --> 00:55:26,919
It was the scariest
funniest day

450
00:55:27,291 --> 00:55:28,901
I've ever had

451
00:55:29,259 --> 00:55:32,159
Totoro gave us
a lovely present

452
00:55:32,696 --> 00:55:36,236
wrapped in bamboo leaves and
tied with dragon whiskers

453
00:55:37,234 --> 00:55:39,284
When we opened it

454
00:55:39,703 --> 00:55:42,073
it was full of magic nuts
and seeds

455
00:55:46,944 --> 00:55:49,284
We decided to plant them
in the garden

456
00:55:49,746 --> 00:55:51,856
to make a lovely forest

457
00:55:52,282 --> 00:55:54,592
But they haven't sprouted yet

458
00:55:55,052 --> 00:55:58,892
Mei sits there all day
waiting for them

459
00:56:00,958 --> 00:56:04,058
She looks like a little crab

460
00:56:09,633 --> 00:56:11,183
It's nearly summer vacation

461
00:56:11,535 --> 00:56:14,524
Dearest, dear Mom
get well soon

462
00:56:15,072 --> 00:56:16,242
Love, Satsuki

463
00:56:19,276 --> 00:56:20,475
Come on. Bed time

464
00:56:25,249 --> 00:56:25,919
Lights off

465
00:56:26,149 --> 00:56:27,288
Wait, Dad

466
00:56:28,118 --> 00:56:30,748
Daddy, do you think
they will come out tomorrow?

467
00:56:31,255 --> 00:56:34,535
Well, I'm sure
Totoro would know

468
00:56:35,125 --> 00:56:36,355
Good night

469
00:57:25,008 --> 00:57:26,437
Wake up, Mei

470
00:57:44,261 --> 00:57:45,750
That's where
we planted the seeds

471
00:59:18,588 --> 00:59:20,198
Wow, we did it

