what shall 1 do?

510
01:04:31,201 --> 01:04:33,541
Open it
it might be important

511
01:04:37,741 --> 01:04:41,201
PLEASE CONTACT, HOSPITAL

512
01:04:41,811 --> 01:04:42,861
It's from Mom's hospital

513
01:04:43,146 --> 01:04:44,696
