514
01:04:45,048 --> 01:04:50,468
Nanny, What shall ! do?

515
01:04:51,354 --> 01:04:52,904
Calm down

516
01:04:53,256 --> 01:04:55,125
Do you know
where your Dad is?

517
01:04:55,525 --> 01:04:57,135
1 know his office number

518
01:04:57,494 --> 01:04:58,574
But we don't have a telephone

519
01:04:58,862 --> 01:05:00,882
Kanta
take her to use the phone

520
01:05:01,297 --> 01:05:02,757
in the main house

521
01:05:08,338 --> 01:05:10,418
Mei, stay here with me

522
01:05:20,350 --> 01:05:22,220
Stay with Nanny, Mei

523
01:05:59,856 --> 01:06:00,406
Hello

524
01:06:00,623 --> 01:06:02,373
I'd like to make a
long distance call, please

525
01:06:03,426 --> 01:06:06,736
It's Tokyo 31-1382

526
01:06:07,330 --> 01:06:08,000
Yes

527
01:06:09,599 --> 01:06:12,439
A cute girl, Kanta

528
01:06:15,104 --> 01:06:16,154
Hello?

529
01:06:16,439 --> 01:06:17,459
Yes

530
01:06:18,675 --> 01:06:23,685
Hello, may I speak to
Dader. Mr. Kusakabe?

531
01:06:24,514 --> 01:06:25,944
It's his daughter, Satsuki

532
01:06:26,282 --> 01:06:27,482
Yes

533
01:06:30,386 --> 01:06:32,286
Daddy?
It's me, Satsuki

534
01:06:32,689 --> 01:06:33,739
Hello, what's up?

535
01:06:37,427 --> 01:06:38,277
From the hospital?

536
01:06:38,528 --> 01:06:40,928
Okay
Ill call them right away

537
01:06:41,397 --> 01:06:43,917
Is there anything wrong
with Mom?

538
01:06:44,400 --> 01:06:45,330
Don't worry

539
01:06:45,602 --> 01:06:50,022
I'll check up and
call you right back

540
01:06:52,342 --> 01:06:54,272
I'm hanging up now
stay there

541
01:06:56,446 --> 01:06:59,786
May I stay here
until he calls back?

542
01:07:01,017 --> 01:07:02,687
Stay as long as you like

543
01:07:10,126 --> 01:07:11,586
Satsuki

544
01:07:20,870 --> 01:07:21,830
No

545
01:07:22,105 --> 01:07:24,005
This corn is for my Mommy

546
01:07:25,642 --> 01:07:28,131
No, it's my Mom's

547
01:07:45,028 --> 01:07:47,928
Listen, Mei
Mom's not well

548
01:07:48,464 --> 01:07:51,094
So she's not coming home
this time

549
01:07:51,601 --> 01:07:52,681
No

550
01:07:54,003 --> 01:07:55,053
