551
01:07:55,338 --> 01:07:57,448
You don't want her
to get worse, do you?

552
01:07:57,874 --> 01:07:59,044
No

553
01:08:00,777 --> 01:08:02,737
It's just for
a few more days

554
01:08:03,146 --> 01:08:04,196
No

555
01:08:05,915 --> 01:08:08,025
So you don't care
if she dies, do you?

556
01:08:08,451 --> 01:08:10,261
No

557
01:08:10,653 --> 01:08:12,613
Stop being silly. I'm going

558
01:08:24,200 --> 01:08:25,309
Let's go, Mei

559
01:08:28,971 --> 01:08:31,721
! hate you, Satsuki

560
01:08:59,202 --> 01:09:01,922
