Don't worry too much, Satsuki

562
01:09:06,175 --> 01:09:09,395
Nanny's here to help
so cheer up

563
01:09:14,082 --> 01:09:16,452
Your Dad said
he'll stop by the hospital

564
01:09:16,919 --> 01:09:18,559
