565
01:09:18,921 --> 01:09:21,581
Besides, it's just a cold

566
01:09:22,091 --> 01:09:25,341
she'll be back next week

567
01:09:30,133 --> 01:09:34,173
They said it was just a cold

568
01:09:34,871 --> 01:09:37,531
when she went into hospital

569
01:09:38,041 --> 01:09:39,821
But what if she dies

570
01:09:40,209 --> 01:09:42,169
Dont be silly, Satsuki

571
01:09:42,578 --> 01:09:44,308
