pretty little girls like you

574
01:09:56,325 --> 01:09:59,575
There, there
Don't cry

575
01:10:00,163 --> 01:10:03,503
I'll be here until
Daddy comes back, okay?

576
01:10:46,876 --> 01:10:49,246
Mei

577
01:10:54,150 --> 01:10:55,700
Mei

