That's strange

582
01:11:11,000 --> 01:11:12,460
Where has she gone?

583
01:11:12,802 --> 01:11:14,472
! was nasty to her

584
01:11:14,837 --> 01:11:16,447
‘cause she was being silly

585
01:11:16,806 --> 01:11:19,026
Maybe she's heading
for the hospital

586
01:11:19,475 --> 01:11:22,345
The hospital?

587
01:11:22,879 --> 01:11:25,068
It would take
a grown up three hours

588
01:11:25,515 --> 01:11:26,565
Ill go look

589
01:11:28,117 --> 01:11:30,307
Kanta, hurry

590
01:11:30,753 --> 01:11:32,152
Tell your dad

591
01:11:32,488 --> 01:11:34,858
that Mei is missing

592
01:11:44,033 --> 01:11:46,223
Stupid Mei
Always getting lost

593
01:11:54,510 --> 01:11:56,260
Mei

594
01:12:03,553 --> 01:12:05,363
Excuse me

595
01:12:07,456 --> 01:12:09,886
Have you seen
a little girl pass by?

596
01:12:10,359 --> 01:12:11,789
She's my sister

597
01:12:12,128 --> 01:12:14,468
No, ! don't think so

598
01:12:14,931 --> 01:12:16,891
I'm sure I would've noticed

599
01:12:18,501 --> 01:12:19,871
Maybe she wasn't here

600
01:12:39,555 --> 01:12:41,335
Are you sure
she came this way?

601
01:12:41,724 --> 01:12:42,864
I don't know

602
01:12:51,767 --> 01:12:53,727
Mei

603
01:13:15,224 --> 01:13:16,774
Please, stop

604
01:13:19,662 --> 01:13:20,682
Jerk. What are you doing?

605
01:13:20,963 --> 01:13:22,072
I'm looking for my sister

606
01:13:22,365 --> 01:13:24,005
Have you seen a little girl?

607
01:13:24,867 --> 01:13:25,857
Your little sister?

608
01:13:26,135 --> 01:13:27,625
She's four

609
01:13:27,970 --> 01:13:29,900
! think she's heading
to the hospital

610
01:13:30,306 --> 01:13:31,446
Did you see anyone?

611
01:13:31,741 --> 01:13:34,931
No. We just came from there

612
01:13:35,511 --> 01:13:37,321
but we didn't see anyone

613
01:13:38,381 --> 01:13:40,281
Thanks anyway

614
01:13:41,250 --> 01:13:42,770
Where have you come from?

615
01:13:43,119 --> 01:13:43,989
From Matsugo

616
01:13:44,253 --> 01:13:45,623
Really?

617
01:13:45,955 --> 01:13:47,475
Good luck

618
01:13:49,191 --> 01:13:50,151
See you

619
01:14:01,737 --> 01:14:03,347
Satsuki

620
01:14:04,907 --> 01:14:06,397
Kanta

621
01:14:08,177 --> 01:14:09,166
Find her?
No

622
01:14:09,445 --> 01:14:10,615
And you?

623
01:14:11,347 --> 01:14:13,246
Dad and the others
are looking for her

624
01:14:13,649 --> 01:14:15,399
I'll go to the hospital

625
01:14:15,785 --> 01:14:17,305
you go back home

626
01:14:17,653 --> 01:14:18,963
I guess she got lost

627
01:14:19,288 --> 01:14:21,598
on the way to the hospital

628
01:14:22,058 --> 01:14:24,668
They found
a sandal by the pond

629
01:14:32,134 --> 01:14:34,244
We're not sure
if it's hers or not

630
01:14:52,154 --> 01:14:53,384
Did you find her?

631
01:15:25,187 --> 01:15:28,967
Dear Lord
please protect her and...

632
01:15:29,625 --> 01:15:32,115
It's too deep here
better search further away

633
01:15:32,595 --> 01:15:34,525
Hey, are there any poles left?

634
01:15:43,339 --> 01:15:45,149
Grandma, Satsuki's here

635
01:15:50,112 --> 01:15:51,572
Nanny

636
01:15:52,982 --> 01:15:54,472
Look, is it hers?

637
01:16:04,226 --> 01:16:05,335
No, it isn't

638
01:16:16,038 --> 01:16:17,647
Thank heavens

639
01:16:18,007 --> 01:16:21,076
! was sure it was hers

640
01:16:21,644 --> 01:16:23,984
Hey, Nanny was jumping
fo conclusions

641
01:16:24,447 --> 01:16:25,937
It's not hers

642
01:16:26,282 --> 01:16:27,832
Where's she gone then?

643
01:16:28,184 --> 01:16:29,444
Let's start from scratch

644
01:16:29,752 --> 01:16:31,212
We better hurry
it'll be dark soon

645
01:16:31,554 --> 01:16:35,244
l really appreciate
your help, everyone

646
01:17:05,387 --> 01:17:07,967
Please, help me Totoro

647
01:17:08,457 --> 01:17:11,417
Mei is lost
It'll be dark soon

648
01:17:11,961 --> 01:17:13,981
I'm sure
she's scared somewhere

649
01:17:45,227 --> 01:17:46,217
Totoro

650
01:17:48,297 --> 01:17:50,406
Totoro, Mei is lost

651
01:17:50,833 --> 01:17:52,353
and we can‘t find her

652
01:17:52,701 --> 01:17:54,981
She must be scared

653
01:17:55,905 --> 01:17:58,125
please help me find her

654
01:17:59,508 --> 01:18:01,438
1 don't know what fo do

655
01:19:00,769 --> 01:19:02,319
They can't see the bus

656
01:19:49,985 --> 01:19:52,005
“FOREST-SWAMP"

657
01:19:52,421 --> 01:19:54,641
“CEMETERY-SHRINE“

658
01:19:55,090 --> 01:19:57,900
"MEI"

659
01:20:14,243 --> 01:20:16,823
Mei...

660
01:20:25,954 --> 01:20:27,414
The trees are
moving out of the way

661
01:20:59,254 --> 01:21:00,594
Mei

662
01:21:04,727 --> 01:21:09,997
Satsuki...

663
01:21:10,866 --> 01:21:12,126
Mei

664
01:21:21,643 --> 01:21:23,923
Mei Satsuki

665
01:21:27,649 --> 01:21:28,439
You silly girl

666
01:21:28,684 --> 01:21:29,994
I'm sorry

667
01:21:32,855 --> 01:21:35,575
You wanted to
take the corn to Mom?

668
01:21:44,400 --> 01:21:46,179
“HOSPITAL”

669
01:21:48,303 --> 01:21:49,823
Will you take us
to the hospital?

670
01:21:52,775 --> 01:21:53,915
Thank you so much

671
01:22:03,285 --> 01:22:04,275
I'm sorry

672
01:22:04,553 --> 01:22:07,803
They didn't need to send
a telegram just for a cold

673
01:22:08,390 --> 01:22:10,580
The girls must be worried

674
01:22:11,026 --> 01:22:12,635
I'm sorry to upset them

675
01:22:12,995 --> 01:22:15,305
They'll be fine

676
01:22:15,764 --> 01:22:16,754
As long as you're okay

677
01:22:17,032 --> 01:22:18,642
We've all learned to cope

678
01:22:19,001 --> 01:22:20,781
This'll just postpone
the enjoyment

679
01:22:22,504 --> 01:22:25,464
They've put up with it so well

680
01:22:26,008 --> 01:22:27,588
I'm especially sorry
for Satsuki

681
01:22:27,943 --> 01:22:29,673
she's so sensitive

682
01:22:30,045 --> 01:22:31,685
You're right

683
01:22:32,047 --> 01:22:34,126
I'm going to spoil them
for a while

684
01:22:34,550 --> 01:22:36,130
when I come home

685
01:22:36,485 --> 01:22:37,565
Oh no

686
01:22:44,693 --> 01:22:46,093
She's laughing

687
01:22:46,428 --> 01:22:48,157
Looks like she's fine

688
01:22:56,638 --> 01:22:59,298
1 can't wait to
get back on my feet

689
01:23:01,343 --> 01:23:02,543
Look

690
01:23:08,784 --> 01:23:10,013
Where did that come from?

691
01:23:12,254 --> 01:23:13,514
What?

692
01:23:13,822 --> 01:23:15,252
! could swear
! just saw Satsuki

693
01:23:15,591 --> 01:23:17,491
and Mei laughing up
in that tree

694
01:23:20,462 --> 01:23:21,982
Maybe they were too

695
01:23:22,331 --> 01:23:26,021
Look
“For Mother"

